ActHistoric Sites and Monuments Act
PrecisAppointment of SHANNON LEWIS-SIMPSON of Harbour Main, Newfoundland and Labrador, to be a member of the Historic Sites and Monuments Board of Canada, as a representative of the Province of Newfoundland and Labrador, to hold office during pleasure for a period of five years, effective June 18, 2017.
